<h1>Alert</h1>
<p>Container for escalated messages.</p>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
  <template>
    <m-alert type="info" autodismiss>Important message</m-alert>
    <m-alert type="success">Reassuring message</m-alert>
    <m-alert type="warn">Cautionary message</m-alert>
    <m-alert type="error">Error message</m-alert>
  </template>
</code-sample>
<h2 id="api">API</h2>
<h3 id="tag">Tag</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Type</th>
    <th>Content</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <td><code>m-alert</code></td>
    <td>Custom Element</td>
    <td>Any</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="attributes">Attributes</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Value</th>
    <th>Required</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <td><code>type</code></td>
    <td>
      <ul type="none">
        <li>info <span class="fnt-bold fnt-italic">default</span></li>
        <li>success</li>
        <li>warn</li>
        <li>error</li>
      </ul>
    </td>
    <td></td>
    <td>Sets the type of the message.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><code>autodismiss</code></td>
    <td>Boolean attribute or Number</td>
    <td></td>
    <td>When present the Alert will automatically be removed after 4 seconds. To increase/decrease the duration set its value to the desired number of seconds.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><code>dismissible</code></td>
    <td>
      <ul type="none">
        <li>true <span class="fnt-italic fnt-bold">default</span></li>
        <li>false</li>
      </ul>
    </td>
    <td></td>
    <td>When set to "false" the dismiss button will not be displayed so the user can't dismiss the Alert. The application can still directly remove the Alert from the DOM or call its <code>dismiss</code> method.</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="events">Events</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Detail</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <td><code>m-dismiss</code></td>
    <td>None</td>
    <td>Fired after Alert is removed from the DOM.</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="methods">Methods</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>Signature</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <td><code>dismiss()</code></td>
    <td>Removes the Alert from the DOM.</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
